    Class Description
    DeadEvent
    An object that is indirectly posted whenever an event without any listening subscribers is posted.
    DispatchErrorHandler
    A DispatchErrorHandler may be used to handle errors that occur while dispatching an event to a subscriber.
    Event
    The base interface for all events that can be posted to an EventBus.
    EventBus<E extends Event>
    An EventBus for publish-subscribe-style communication between components.
    EventBus.Builder<E extends Event>
    A builder class for an EventBus.
    EventBus.Subscriber<E extends Event>
    A wrapper class for a subscriber method.
    EventDispatcher
    An object that takes care of submitting events to subscribers.
    EventSubscriber
    Default marker for EventBus subscribers.
    MJLExecutors
    A collection of executors that are commonly used with an EventBus.
    NonNullApi
    Do NOT use this interface in external code.
